title: Integrate QR code library

title: Build card preview feature

title: Create sharing functionality

title: Set up user analytics
description: Implement tracking to gather data on card views and shares.

title: User feedback form

title: Conduct usability testing

title: Optimize for mobile

title: Finalize UI design
description: Complete the UI design for all screens and components of the webapp.

title: Implement user profile management
description: Allow users to edit their profile and update their card information.

title: Prepare deployment script
description: Create a deployment script to automate the deployment process to the production server.

title: Launch marketing campaign
description: Plan and execute a marketing campaign to promote the launch of the webapp.
